::KitKat::

She was proud of her accomplishments. But she wasn't one to advertise 
her capabilities.  Not like Sisesis and Sinester.  She didn't mind 
showing old battle scars.  But she wasn't one to gloat over what she 
had done.
"It wasn't really anything.  He got in my way and I asked him to 
move.  He didn't want to so I made him move."  She trotted off to the 
CR chambers.
